title: Hydrostatics, Optics, Sound and Heat
author: Isaac Newton
abstract:
This large accumulation of papers dates from about 1672-1706. It includes drafts of his book on Opticks and other miscellaneous writings. The Contents tab provides some navigation for these papers, as does the record in the Library’s archives catalogue.

Transcriptions are available for a small selection of papers within this manuscript.
